Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部直达高度紧急时态用命令传达线路维护性检查任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字很让人吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务非常重要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的话可能导致全小队一起受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据情况不同还可能启动第一类警戒状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近卫在内的全师团都会进入紧急出动的准备状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对  任务极其重大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这个电话是连接首都司令部的热线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听到它响过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢  很幸运的还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  虽然希望它不叫  但不会希望它该叫的时候不叫吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每半年一次  会做检查以确认连接情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部直达紧急时  …嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是司令部直达高度紧急时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是司令部直达高度紧急时态用命令传达线路维护性检查任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是是  请把这个任务交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就想试试用电话交谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用得着那么兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本和建御雷神的对讲机感觉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这个距离更远一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真厉害  能和那么远的人交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  和样子都看不见的人交谈是有点神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但习惯的话就没什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一个问题是今天不知道对方会什么时候打来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那么今天你就一整天好好守着电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮铃铃  这里是赫尔维西亚陆军第1121号要塞空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  电话完后记得放回原处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲  菲  菲利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利西娅前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干嘛啊  不闷得慌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点火车要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火车？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有文件急需交到总部去  克劳斯要下周才会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要去车站  电话就交给你负责了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一没接听到  最严重可能会被判断为我们遭到了袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好守着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我没有睡  真的没有在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到乃绘留吗  房间里没找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是机库吗  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  中午想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  是轮到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  为什么暮羽和你一轮到我做饭就要跟我抢着干？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们来前我可是常做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道也是不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  味道比起外观要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  味道很明确  真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  那我今天就比平时再加把劲去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  娜奥美大姐在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得守着电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  来招呼客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想再吃那混有菜板碎片的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧  苹果苏打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是卖我们苹果汁的农家亲手制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个能算是我们的苹果酒的近亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对呢  你已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰问品要两瓶就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰问品？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天商业工会成员要聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时很受他们照顾  送慰问品是一直来的惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊什么啊  她们一直以来瞒的那么费劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有机会再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说那个  娜奥美大姐也一起吃午饭吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  叫我也去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周报纸上的那新闻你看了吧  大家都希望能直接从军人那里听到说明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那休战协议的签订遇到困难什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赔偿金的多少领土的划分等等拖拖拉拉定不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这也是常见的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  工会的那些大叔真正目的只是想见见你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从泼水节扮演炎之女后  你的Fans那增加的速度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦人  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  看来我得去一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身心都已经是碉堡的少女了  一个人也一定能完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  就交给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉是我用过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…小号的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒真棒  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的喇叭也越吹越好了  这是给坚持练习的你的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有了这个就不会打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个是C D E F G
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天  要结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了  晒的衣服会弄湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子也在作战行动范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  出来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方  出来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮我
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  衣服没事就最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  一来就让你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放在心上  我们突然到访才不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明天要回到特雷兹  特意前来打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没必要向军队打招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话不能这么说  塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说前段时间这孩子也对你们无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺道想在此道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫梨旺小姐吗  那位黑头发的小姐也出门了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  还想见上一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这本书是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小号的书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梨旺前辈给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  真是失礼了  自说自话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方一个人留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部直达高度紧急时态用命令传达线路维护性检查任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…执行中的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说  等这个响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我是第一次用  心里有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心能不能说好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美娜小姐也去了工会的集会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  去接受工会各位的捐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  请尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝是喝  别以为这样就能拉拢我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米希欧你们知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的是电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了逗孩子们开心  我有时会做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害  好厉害啊  塞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  首先得说「喂喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是打电话的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  真的能听见声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是赫尔维西亚陆军第1121号要塞空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  放松些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您百忙之中抽空致电真是过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  放松些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  鸟先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米希欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  米希欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  司祭大人和孩子们来这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:17:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  诸神灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是来道歉与告辞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然顾着玩耍给人家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罚你们没晚饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的衣服都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  还有替换…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个好提议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  太难为情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会  多么漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是谢谢由美娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会洗完后还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对孩子们来说太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我想没有人比彼方更适合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会陪我玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞亚下次也要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有空就来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿诸神保佑你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记要上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群大叔真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  会生病的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直忍着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说她尽职好还是笨拙好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时机抓得也太准了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  这里是赫尔维西亚陆军第1121小队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宫梨旺曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要确认一下你们的线路  所以勉强…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我才没有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚  你没有原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  请拯救这个国家  拯救赫尔维西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘留  难道你一直在这  从早上到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在厕所可以睡得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
